    "body": "Hi, you can set the `export const dynamic = 'force-static';` segment config at the top of your your **[...slug]/page.tsx** file. This will force `headers()` and `useSearchParams()` [to return empty values](https://nextjs.org/docs/app/api-reference/file-conventions/route-segment-config#dynamic:~:text=dynamicParams%20%3D%20true.-,%27force%2Dstatic%27,to%20return%20empty%20values.,-Good%20to%20know) when used during static prerendering.",
